businessinsider.com%2Faustralian-couple-built-hotel-indonesian-island-sumba-2023-10%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eisland%20of%20Sumba.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20natural%20beauty%2C%20lack%20of%20traffic%2C%20and%20smaller%20number%20of%20tourists%20made%20for%20a%20great%20getaway.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20my%20flexible%20schedule%20and%20spend%20two%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-family-kids-bali-decompress-relocate-slow-life-work-remote-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emonths%20in%20Bali%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20working%20remotely%20and%20exploring%20the%20island.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20already%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-vacationed-bali-18-family-members-a-disaster-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evisited%20Bali%3C%2Fa%3E%20many%20times%2C%20and%20I'm%20a%20big%20fan.%20But%20over%20the%20years%2C%20as%20its%20fame%20has%20spread%2C%20it%20has%20become%20busier.%20Bali's%20iconic%20charm%20and%20unique%20energy%20are%20still%20there%2C%20but%20they%20now%20coexist%20with%20big%20crowds%20and%20heavy%20traffic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%20time%20there%2C%20I%20relished%20much%20of%20what%20Bali%20has%20to%20offer%3A%20yoga%2C%20massages%2C%20sound%20baths%2C%20authentic%20spiritual%20traditions%2C%20gorgeous%20style%2C%20and%20delicious%20food.%20I%20found%20pockets%20away%20from%20the%20crowds%20in%20the%20less-developed%20regions%20of%20Bangli%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgreat-trip-bali-skipping-popular-areas-saving-money-sidemen-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESidemen%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20after%20a%20few%20weeks%20in%20Ubud%20and%20south%20Bali%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20craving%20peace%20and%20quiet%20%E2%80%94%20specifically%2C%20a%20break%20from%20the%20ever-present%20sound%20of%20motorbike%20engines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%2C%20I%20had%20planned%20to%20wrap%20up%20my%20time%20in%20Indonesia%20with%20a%20weeklong%20side%20trip%20to%20the%20nearby%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-couple-created-cap-karoso-luxury-resort-sumba-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eisland%20of%20Sumba%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20friend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bd1ebca1-9f8a-491e-be79-1a5f2633248b%5C%22%3EOverpopulation%20was%20no%20longer%20a%20problem%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESumba%20is%20a%2090-minute%20direct%20flight%20from%20Denpasar%20International%20Airport.%20It's%20about%20twice%20the%20size%20of%20Bali%2C%20has%20one-sixth%20of%20Bali's%20population%2C%20and%20a%20fraction%20of%20its%20tourists.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20known%20for%20limited%20WiFi%20and%20cell%20service%20across%20large%20swaths%20of%20its%20undeveloped%20territory.%20There's%20no%20signage%20on%20the%20main%20roads%20indicating%20the%20island's%20scenic%20spots%2C%20making%20it%20hard%20for%20visitors%20to%20find%20them%20without%20a%20local%20guide.%20We%20hired%20a%20guide%20my%20friend%20found%20through%20Facebook%2C%20and%20we're%20glad%20we%20did.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20standing%20in%20a%20bikini%20under%20a%20waterfall%20in%20Sumba%2C%20Indonesia.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68426ed39d73a0031e8e0095%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221620%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20visited%20sandy%20coves%20and%20waterfalls%20in%20Sumba.%3Cp%3ESonya%20Moore%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESumba's%20natural%20beauty%20lived%20up%20to%20our%20expectations.%20The%20rock-framed%20sandy%20coves%2C%20the%20turquoise%20lagoon%2C%20the%20landscapes%20of%20velvety%20green%20hills%2C%20and%20the%20waterfalls%20left%20my%20friend%20and%20me%20in%20awe.%20We%20were%20charmed%20by%20goats%20lounging%20by%20the%20side%20of%20the%20road%20and%20by%20horses%20meandering%20across%20expanses%20of%20golden%20savannah.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20most%20of%20the%20time%2C%20we%20had%20the%20sights%20all%20to%20ourselves.%20Sometimes%2C%20groups%20of%20local%20kids%20would%20come%20over%20to%20talk%20to%20us.%20The%20roads%20were%20free%20of%20traffic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Horses%20near%20the%20Puru%20Kambera%20Savannah%2C%20on%20the%20eastern%20side%20of%20Sumba%20Island.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68429839c19ab3675c10c79c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHorses%20were%20spotted%20near%20the%20Puru%20Kambera%20Savannah%20on%20the%20eastern%20side%20of%20Sumba%20Island.%3Cp%3ESonya%20Moore%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20the%20absence%20of%20tourists%20and%20traffic%20came%20the%20absence%20of%20extensive%20food%20and%20massage%20options%2C%20which%20we%20had%20grown%20accustomed%20to%20in%20Bali.%20I%20never%20found%20wine%20or%20cocktails%20anywhere%20in%20Sumba%2C%20though%20I%20imagine%20they're%20available%20at%20the%20handful%20of%205-star%20hotels%20on%20the%20island.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-people-on-this-remote-indonesian-island-still-practice-blood-sacrifice-2015-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epeople%20in%20Sumba%3C%2Fa%3E%20didn't%20speak%20much%20English%2C%20including%20our%20guide%2C%20so%20we%20needed%20translation%20apps%20to%20communicate%20most%20of%20the%20time.%20When%20there%20was%20no%20cell%20service%2C%20we%20had%20to%20resort%20to%20hand%20gestures.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20punctuality%3F%20We%20found%20out%20that%20it's%20not%20a%20thing%20in%20Sumba.%20Our%20driver%20tended%20to%20show%20up%2015%20to%2020%20minutes%20after%20our%20agreed%20departure%20time%2C%20then%20order%20himself%20a%20coffee%20before%20we%20left%2C%20then%20stop%20to%20pick%20up%20his%20breakfast%20at%20a%20roadside%20shop%20or%20get%20gas.%20He%20was%20an%20excellent%20drone%20videographer%20and%20photographer%2C%20though%2C%20which%20helped%20make%20up%20for%20his%20relaxed%20sense%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ae969d8c-e985-40ac-ab54-ebe960a7ac2e%5C%22%3EA%20true%20mental%20reset%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20four-day%20guided%20Sumba%20road%20trip%20covered%20a%20lot%20of%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20road%20trip%2C%20we%20spent%20three%20nights%20at%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkoh-samui-beach-hotel-cielo-owner-thailand-renovate-raise-family-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eboutique%20hotel%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20a%20deserted%20stretch%20of%20white%20sand%20beach%20in%20East%20Sumba%2C%20about%20an%20hour%20from%20the%20airport%2C%20and%20it%20was%20there%20that%20we%20found%20total%20relaxation.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShaded%20by%20tall%20cemara%20trees%2C%20the%20temperature%20was%20perfect%20both%20day%20and%20night.%20We%20were%20lulled%20to%20sleep%20every%20night%20by%20the%20sound%20of%20gentle%20ocean%20waves%20lapping%20the%20shore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20in%20a.%20red%20bikini%20floating%20in%20the%20Waikuri%20Lagoon%20in%20Sumbai%2C%20Indonesia.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68426f95c19ab3675c10c73c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20friend%20floating%20in%20the%20Waikuri%20Lagoon.%3Cp%3ESonya%20Moore%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20hotel%2C%20Cemara%20Beachfront%20Suite%2C%20was%20%2480%20per%20night%20and%20came%20with%20great%20service.%20The%20staff%20brought%20us%20tea%20with%20little%20desserts%20every%20afternoon%20and%20were%20always%20ready%20to%20provide%20any%20extras%20we%20asked%20for%20to%20make%20our%20stay%20more%20enjoyable.%20Except%20wine.%20Next%20time%2C%20I'd%20bring%20a%20bottle%20or%20two%20in%20my%20suitcase%2C%20along%20with%20a%20good%20book.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20attentive%20care%20of%20the%20staff%20and%20the%20idyllic%20setting%20allowed%20us%20to%20completely%20unwind%20and%20fully%20enjoy%20just%20being%20there.%20We%20could%20have%20happily%20stayed%20much%20longer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESumba's%20wild%20beauty%20and%20serene%20relaxation%20provided%20the%20perfect%20complement%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdream-trip-to-bali-disappointing-changed-plans-save-it-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBali%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsumba-indonesia-island-getaway-from-bali-relax-beach-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749428041000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68426b259d73a0031e8e0083%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsumba-indonesia-island-getaway-from-bali-relax-beach-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22She%20spent%20two%20months%20working%20remotely%20from%20Bali.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20her%20trip%2C%20she%20traveled%20to%20Sumba%2C%20a%20nearby%20island.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Sonya%20Moore)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsumba-indonesia-island-getaway-from-bali-relax-beach-2025-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%E2%80%99s%20LA%20crackdown%3A%20Hundreds%20of%20National%20Guard%20troops%20deployed%3B%20protesters%20block%20freeway%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749427294000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-121714804%2Cimgsize-1125113.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fdonald-trumps-la-crackdown-hundreds-of-national-guard-troops-deployed-protesters-flood-streets-key-developments