a%20from%20over%2050%20of%20the%202%2C000%20recipients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20report%20outlined%20nearly%20a%20dozen%20key%20impacts%20reported%20by%20program%20recipients%2C%20Dagg%20highlighted%20five%20major%20takeaways%20during%20the%20Zoom%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDagg%20said%20that%20recipients%20who%20received%20money%20from%20the%20program%20reported%20more%20stability%20and%20%26quot%3Bsignificantly%20reduced%26quot%3B%20financial%20stress.%20It%20relieved%20their%20anxiety%20about%20fulfilling%20their%20basic%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParticipating%20in%20the%20pilot%20program%20also%20allowed%20artists%20to%20re-prioritize%20how%20they%20spend%20their%20time%20and%20what%20they%20choose%20to%20focus%20on.%20%26quot%3BThe%20opportunity%20to%20focus%20more%20on%20their%20specific%20creative%20interests%20opened%20new%20possibilities%20and%20career%20trajectories%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArtists%20said%20the%20added%20income%20allowed%20them%20to%20spend%20more%20time%20%26quot%3Bresearching%2C%20experimenting%2C%20taking%20risks%2C%20and%20failing%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20has%20improved%20the%20quality%20of%20their%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArtists%2C%20the%20report%20said%2C%20also%20felt%20more%20confident%20in%20themselves%20and%20their%20work%20during%20the%20program.%20%26quot%3BMany%20recipients%20talk%20of%20feeling%20empowered%2C%20of%20being%20in%20control%20of%20the%20choices%20within%20their%20lives%2C%20and%20envisioning%20a%20viable%20career%20path%20longer-term%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecipients%20even%20reported%20better%20mental%20health%2C%20which%20led%20to%20improved%20sleep%20quality%20and%20lowered%20stress%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f63e524f-bbec-48b6-a49f-62ed75937838%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20next%20for%20Ireland's%20basic%20income%20program%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20end%20of%20the%20program%20fast%20approaching%2C%20recipients%20of%20the%20weekly%20payment%20are%20reckoning%20with%20what%20how%20their%20lives%20might%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAcross%20art%20forms%2C%20recipients%20report%20concerns%20about%20financial%20stability%20and%20sustaining%20the%20momentum%20of%20their%20careers%20when%2C%20or%20if%2C%20the%20basic%20income%20scheme%20ends%2C%26quot%3B%20Dagg's%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20month%2C%20Basic%20Income%20Ireland%20called%20on%20the%20government%20to%20immediately%20implement%20a%20universal%20and%20unconditional%20basic%20income%20for%20the%20country.%20A%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20UBI%20Lab%20Network%20said%20the%20pilot%20program's%20success%20shows%20that%20basic%20income%20is%20a%20viable%20option.%20The%20campaign%20group%20shared%20a%20proposal%20for%20introducing%20a%20universal%20basic%20income%20to%20Ireland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20the%20pilot%20shows%2C%20basic%20income%20works%20and%20people%20need%20a%20UBI%20now%20to%20face%20and%20deal%20with%20the%20many%20social%2C%20economic%2C%20and%20ecological%20crises%20of%20our%20world.%20The%20Network%20will%20continue%20to%20help%20demonstrate%20basic%20income%20within%20communities%20and%20show%20how%20it%20is%20a%20sustainable%20policy%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatrick%20O'Donovan%2C%20Ireland's%20minister%20for%20arts%20and%20culture%2C%C2%A0said%20he%20would%20evaluate%20the%20data%20collected%20throughout%20the%20pilot%20program%20and%20create%20proposals%20for%20the%20government%20regarding%20the%20next%20steps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20heartened%20by%20the%20responses%20of%20the%20Basic%20Income%20recipients%20in%20this%20paper%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Donovan%20said%20in%20the%20May%20report.%20%26quot%3BThis%20research%20will%20add%20to%20the%20evaluation%20being%20conducted%20by%20my%20department%2C%20which%20to%20date%20clearly%20shows%20that%20the%20Basic%20Income%20Pilot%20has%20been%20an%20effective%20support%20for%20the%20artists%20in%2