0that%20AI%20will%20come%20for%20human%20jobs%2C%20added%20that%20AI%20had%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20%26quot%3Befficiency%20gains%26quot%3B%20at%20Klarna%20and%20that%20the%20firm's%20workforce%20had%20shrunk%20from%20about%205%2C500%20to%203%2C000%20people%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years%20as%20a%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20the%20first%20time%20the%20exec%20and%20Klarna%20have%20made%20headlines%20along%20these%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202024%2C%20Klarna%20boasted%20that%20its%20OpenAI-powered%20AI%20assistant%20was%20doing%20the%20work%20of%20700%20full-time%20customer%20service%20agents.%20The%20company%2C%20most%20famous%20for%20its%20%26quot%3Bbuy%20now%2C%20pay%20later%26quot%3B%20service%2C%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20firms%20to%20partner%20with%20Sam%20Altman's%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%20that%20year%2C%20Siemiatkowski%20told%20Bloomberg%20TV%20that%20he%20believed%20AI%20was%20already%20capable%20of%20doing%20%26quot%3Ball%20of%20the%20jobs%26quot%3B%20that%20humans%20do%20and%20that%20Klarna%20had%20enacted%20a%20hiring%20freeze%20since%202023%20as%20it%20looked%20to%20slim%20down%20and%20focus%20on%20adopting%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Siemiatkowski%20has%20since%20dialed%20back%20his%20all-in%20stance%20on%20AI%2C%20telling%20an%20audience%20at%20the%20firm's%20Stockholm%20headquarters%20in%20May%20that%20his%20AI-driven%20customer%20service%20cost-cutting%20efforts%20had%20gone%20too%20far%20and%20that%20Klarna%20was%20planning%20to%20now%20recruit%2C%20according%20to%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20a%20brand%20perspective%2C%20a%20company%20perspective%2C%20I%20just%20think%20it's%20so%20critical%20that%20you%20are%20clear%20to%20your%20customer%20that%20there%20will%20be%20always%20a%20human%20if%20you%20want%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20interview%20with%20The%20Times%2C%20Siemiatkowski%20said%20he%20felt%20that%20many%20people%20in%20the%20tech%20i