C%224066%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EArk%20Invest%20CEO%20Cathie%20Wood%20says%20the%20feud%20between%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20Elon%20Musk%20shows%20just%20how%20much%20the%20latter's%20companies%20rely%20on%20the%20government.%3Cp%3EJoe%20Raedle%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EArk%20Invest's%20Cathie%20Wood%20has%20weighed%20in%20on%20the%20public%20feud%20between%20Elon%20Musk%20and%20Donald%20Trump.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWood%20said%20the%20feud%20reveals%20how%20much%20Musk's%20companies%20rely%20on%20the%20US%20government.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETrump%20said%20Saturday%20he%20had%20no%20desire%20to%20fix%20his%20relationship%20with%20the%20Tesla%20CEO.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-elon-musk-fight-takeaways-tesla-spacex-ai-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epublic%20feud%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20Elon%20Musk%20and%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20shown%20investors%20just%20how%20much%20control%20the%20US%20government%20has%20over%20Musk's%20companies%2C%20Ark%20Invest%20CEO%20Cathie%20Wood%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20way%20this%20is%20evolving%20is%20Elon%2C%20Tesla%2C%20and%20investors%20are%20beginning%20to%20understand%20more%20and%20more%20just%20how%20much%20the%20government%20has%20control%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Wood%20said%20in%20a%20video%20posted%20to%20the%20company's%20YouTube%20channel%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20Musk's%20companies%20have%20key%20links%20to%20the%20government%20and%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-list-government-subsidies-tesla-billions-spacex-solarcity-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereceived%20billions%20of%20dollars%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20federal%20loans%2C%20contracts%2C%20tax%20credits%2C%20and%20subsidies%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BElon%20is%20involved%20in%20companies%20that%20are%20depending%20on%20the%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20Wood%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20Tesla%2C%20SpaceX%2C%20and%20Neuralink%20as%20examples.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpaceX's%20COO%2C%20Gwynne%20Shotwell%2C%20said%20last%20year%20that%20the%20company%20has%20%2422%20billion%20worth%20of%20federal%20contracts.%20Neuralink%2C%20Musk's%20brain%20chip%20company%2C%20is%20subject%20to%20FDA%20regulation%2C%20and%20a%20less%20friendly%20regulatory%20environment%20could%20impact%20Tesla's%20robotaxi%20rollout%20plans.%20Tesla%20stock%20fell%20more%20than%2014%25%20on%20Thursday%20after%20Musk%20and%20Trump%20became%20locked%20in%20a%20series%20of%20increasingly%20bitter%20clashes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20feud%20appeared%20to%20begin%2C%20at%20least%20publicly%2C%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20after%20Musk%20criticized%20Trump's%20%26quot%3BOne%20Big%20Beautiful%20Bill.%26quot%3B%20He%20called%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bdisgusting%20abomination%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20it%20would%20increase%20the%20national%20budget%20deficit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETensions%20rose%20fast%20between%20the%20once-close%20allies%20on%20Thursday.%20Trump%20threatened%20to%20cut%20Musk's%20government%20contracts%20and%20Musk%20said%20SpaceX%20would%20immediately%20begin%20decommissioning%20its%20Dragon%20spacecraft%20%E2%80%94%20which%20returned%20stranded%20NASA%20astronauts%20Suni%20Williams%20and%20Butch%20Wilmore%20from%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20later%20retracted%20that%20threat%2C%20which%20Wood%20said%20was%20a%20sign%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bbeginning%20to%20walk%20this%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWood%20said%20the%20rift%20with%20Trump%20could%2C%20in%20part%2C%20be%20Musk's%20attempt%20to%20further%20decouple%20himself%20from%20the%20Trump%20administration.%20Musk%20announced%20in%20April%20that%20he%20would%20be%20stepping%20back%20from%20his%20government%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20hypotheses%20out%20there%20is%20that%20what%20has%20happened%20was%20partly%20%E2%80%94%20not%20entirely%20%E2%80%94%20orchestrated%2C%26quot%3B%20Wood%20said.%20%26quot%3BClearly%2C%20there%20has%20been%20some%20brand%20damage%20to%20Tesla%2C%20which%20he%20readily%20admits%2C%20and%20I%20think%20he's%20trying%20to%20disengage%20from%20the%20government%20and%20being%20associated%20with%20one%20party%20or%20the%20other.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoving%20forward%2C%20Wood%20said%20neither%20Trump%20nor%20Musk%20needed%20to%20get%20%26quot%3Bbogged%20down%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20fight%20and%20that%20she%20believed%20both%20would%20eventually%20heed%20that%20reasoning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20appeared%20to%20be%20confident%20that%20Musk%20could%20make%20the%20situation%20work%20for%20him.%20She%20said%20Musk%20%26quot%3Bworks%20really%20well%20under%20pressure%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bhe%20creates%20a%20lot%20of%20that%20chaos%20and%20pressure%20himself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%2C%20however%2C%20signaled%20Saturday%20that%20he%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-elon-musk-relationship-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eno%20desire%20to%20fix%20his%20relationship%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20SpaceX%20CEO%20anytime%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20no%20intention%20of%20speaking%20to%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20told%20NBC%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20a%20very%20bad%20thing%2C%20because%20he's%20very%20disrespectful.%20You%20could%20not%20disrespect%20the%20office%20of%20the%20President%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVice%20President%20JD%20Vance%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjd-vance-musk-bitter-feud-trump-huge-mistake-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estruck%20a%20somewhat%20friendlier%20tone%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20reconciliation%20during%20a%20Thursday%20interview%20with%20podcaster%20Theo%20Von.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVance%20said%20that%20while%20he%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20%26quot%