20but%20when%20I%20crunched%20the%20numbers%2C%20it%20didn't%20seem%20like%20such%20a%20great%20value.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20self-proclaimed%20bougie%20backpacker%2C%20I%20love%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraveling-on-50-dollars-a-day-countries-cheap-to-visit%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etraveling%20on%20a%20budget%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I'm%20not%20afraid%20to%20splurge%20on%20unique%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20when%20I%20discovered%20Air%20New%20Zealand's%20Mystery%20Breaks%2C%20I%20was%20instantly%20intrigued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20packages%20include%20round-trip%20flights%2C%20one%20checked%20bag%2C%20accommodations%2C%20breakfast%2C%20and%20airport%20transfers.%20The%20catch%3F%20Your%20destination%20is%20kept%20a%20secret%20until%20two%20days%20before%20departure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAir%20New%20Zealand%20offers%20several%20tiers%2C%20but%20I%20went%20with%20a%20last-minute%20Luxury%20Mystery%20Break.%20This%20top-tier%20package%20includes%20all%20of%20the%20aforementioned%20amenities%2C%20plus%20daily%20dinners%2C%20an%20Avis%20rental%20car%2C%20and%20five-star%20accommodations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20it%20went.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20received%20my%20Mystery%20Break%20itinerary%20a%20few%20days%20before%20my%20travel%20date.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mountains%2C%20trees%20at%20dusk%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682ddefeac40ae2b0c9ea454%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20was%20eager%20to%20explore%20a%20part%20of%20New%20Zealand%20I%20hadn't%20planned%20to%20visit.%3Cp%3EAshley%20Probst%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20booked%20my%20trip%20less%20than%20a%20week%20before%20the%20departure%20date%2C%20but%20a%20Mystery%20Break%20representative%20told%20me%20guests%20are%20encouraged%20to%20reserve%20these%20packages%20three%20to%20six%20months%20