female%20volunteer%20packing%20stuffed%20toys%20in%20boxes%20at%20community%20center%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6740a7adfa0140cdd564e55c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20(not%20pictured)%20trained%20her%20children%20to%20look%20for%20%26quot%3Broadside%20treasures.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EMaskot%2FGetty%20Images%2FMaskot%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20my%20best%20finds%20was%20the%20three%20Cozy%20Coupes%20I%20found%20over%20a%20series%20of%20months%20of%20scouring%20my%20neighborhood%20(because%20you%20can't%20get%20just%20one%20when%20you%20have%20three%20kids%20close%20in%20age).%20Once%20all%20three%20were%20secured%2C%20we%20transformed%20them%2C%20%C3%A0%20la%20Pimp%20My%20Ride%2C%20with%20paint%2C%20decals%2C%20custom%20license%20plates%2C%20and%20streamers%20from%20the%20Dollar%20Tree.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20personalized%20kiddie%20cars%20even%20made%20the%20move%20with%20us%20from%20Illinois%20to%20California%2C%20as%20they%20were%20my%20kids'%20favorites.%20Eventually%2C%20my%20kids%20outgrew%20them%2C%20and%20all%20three%20cars%20were%20scooped%20up%20from%20our%20front%20yard%20%26quot%3Bfree%26quot%3B%20pile%20to%20be%20used%20by%20other%20neighborhood%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2241ed8222-8405-4d09-b017-4f39c6a3af00%5C%22%3EI%20find%20the%20best%20items%20on%20'large%20item'%20pickup%20days%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20now%20live%20in%20the%20San%20Francisco%20Bay%20Area%2C%20adjacent%20to%20some%20bougie%20neighborhoods%2C%20where%20I've%20found%20backyard%20furniture%2C%20an%20antique%20card%20table%2C%20and%20animal-carrying%20cages%20that%20my%20kids%20can%20use%20for%20their%204-H%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESkateboards%20and%20scooters%20are%20often%20discarded%2C%20so%20we've%20collected%20quite%20a%20few%20over%20the%20years%20(and%20then%20donated%20them%20back).%20I%20love%20the%20idea%20that%20these%20items%20are%20j