0helped%20with%20his%20aches%20from%20travel%20and%20working%20out%2C%20but%20the%20plain%20black%20and%20beige%20pairs%20he%20found%20at%20Duane%20Reade%20left%20something%20to%20be%20desired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFerenci%20said%20he%20created%20Comrad%20to%20offer%20a%20%26quot%3Bcompression%20sock%20that%20has%20all%20the%20benefits%20of%20a%20medical%20product%20and%20meets%20all%20the%20requirements%2C%20but%20is%20stylish%20and%20functional%20and%20has%20all%20the%20benefits%20of%20a%20lifestyle%20or%20athletic%20sock%20that%20you%20would%20wear.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225568%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20pair%20of%20compression%20socks.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65256fa16561dd877e760d8c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223712%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20pair%20of%20Comrad%20compression%20socks.%3Cp%3EKatherine%20Frey%2FThe%20Washington%20Post%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFerenci%20told%20BI%20that%20millennials%20make%20up%20most%20of%20Comrad's%20customer%20base%2C%20but%20its%20products%20are%20also%20gaining%20popularity%20with%20Gen%20Z%20shoppers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20major%20player%20is%20Bombas.%20Some%20of%20its%20socks%20are%20designed%20for%20everyday%20wear%2C%20and%20others%20for%20health%20or%20exercise%20support.%20Bombas%20offers%20new%20colors%20and%20patterns%20every%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETam%20Conlin%2C%20Bombas'%20senior%20vice%20president%20of%20merchandising%20and%20design%2C%20told%20BI%20its%20compression%20products%2C%20which%20were%20first%20introduced%20in%202019%2C%20have%20grown%20231%25%20in%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20and%20the%20category%20is%20plus%2031%25%20for%202025%20alone.%20BI%20couldn't%20independently%20confirm%20those%20percentages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConlin%20also%20said%20millennial%20shoppers%20make%20up%20Bombas'%20biggest%20growth%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bombas%20Men's%20Everyday%20Compression%20Sock%203-Pack%20in%20different%20colors.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6548fa5b36d588dc55cb5074%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBombas%20compression%20socks.%3Cp%3EBombas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EConlin%20thinks%20compression%20socks%20are%20resonating%20with%20younger%20consumers%20because%20they%20are%20interested%20in%20%26quot%3Bproducts%20that%20help%20you%20live%20more%20healthfully.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20mindset%20and%20consumer%20behavior%20is%20something%20that's%20really%20been%20taken%20on%20by%20the%20millennial%20generation%20and%20Gen%20Z%2C%20where%20there's%20specific%20products%20for%20specific%20needs%20that%20can%20really%20help%20you%2C%20and%20it's%20kind%20of%20like%20a%20life%20hack%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGarfield%2C%20who%20wears%20Bombas'%20compression%20socks%2C%20said%20the%20look%20is%20a%20game%20changer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20I%20used%20to%20hide%20them%20or%20want%20to%20not%20have%20them%20as%20visible%2C%20but%20they%20just%20look%20like%20socks.%20And%20they're%20cute%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESarabi%20is%20also%20excited%20that%20more%20compression%20products%20are%20on%20the%20market%2C%20particularly%20in%20cuter%20styles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20majority%20of%20healthcare%20systems%2C%20you%20can%20only%20wear%20one%20color%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20if%20you%20could%20bring%20in%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20personality%20to%20design%2C%20it%20makes%20things%20fun.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a64326ca-fad3-419f-b998-6b3223de4c72%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20pick%20the%20right%20compression%20socks%20for%20you%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20tips%20if%20you%20want%20to%20get%20in%20on%20the%20trend%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFind%