ng%20his%20tariffs%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20courts%20strike%20down%20his%20use%20of%20the%20IEEPA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExperts%20in%20international%20trade%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Trump%20could%20take%20four%20different%20routes%20to%20imposing%20trade%20barriers%20without%20Congress.%20All%20four%20are%20doable%2C%20though%20significantly%20more%20complicated%2C%20and%20are%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eunlikely%20policies%20he%20could%20change%20at%20will%20overnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20we're%20over%20a%20hundred%20days%20into%20the%20tariffs%2C%20and%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Etariffs%20are%20a%20very%20top-of-the-agenda%20item%2C%26quot%3B%20Drew%20DeLong%2C%20lead%20in%20geopolitical%20dynamics%20practice%20at%20Kearney%2C%20a%20global%20strategy%20and%20management%20consulting%20firm%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20number%20of%20motivations%20underneath%20tariffs%2C%20and%20whether%20his%20current%20tariffs%20stay%2C%20he%20will%20find%20ways%20to%20continue%20to%20amplify%20pressure%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-world-leaders-have-been-saying-about-trump-tariffs-negotiations-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etrading%20partners%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20DeLong%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmall-businesses-suing-lawsuit-trump-liberation-day-tariffs-ieepa-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esmall%20businesses%3C%2Fa%3E%20sued%20Trump%20and%20his%20various%20trade%20officials%20over%20tariffs%2C%20the%20US%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-tariffs-blocked-federal-court-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECourt%20of%20International%20Trade%3C%2Fa%3E%20ruled%20unanimously%20on%20May%2028%20that%20he%20doesn't%20have%20the%20authority%20to%20levy%20sweeping%20tariffs%20using%20the%20IEEPA%20%E2%80%94%20a%201970s%20law%20typically%20used%20for%20economic%20sanct