ing%20to%20be%20a%20top%20pick%2C%26quot%3B%20Robert%20Shapiro%2C%20an%20attorney%20of%20international%20trade%20at%20Thompson%20Coburn%20LLP%2C%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BThat%20gives%20Trump%20some%20vehicle%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20limited%2015%25%20for%20150%20days%2C%20and%20then%20he%20has%20to%20go%20to%20Congress.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20would%20open%20the%20door%20for%20Congress%20to%20pass%20a%20whole%20bunch%20of%20trade%20actions%2C%20but%20the%20administration%20obviously%20didn't%20want%20to%20go%20through%20that%20first%2C%26quot%3B%20Shapiro%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22064e09f1-95bf-4c3a-b6fc-62cee37f30aa%5C%22%3ESection%20232%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESection%20232%20under%20the%20Trade%20Expansion%20Act%20of%201962%20allows%20the%20White%20House%20to%20raise%20duties%20on%20imports%20it%20deems%20a%20threat%20to%20national%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20probe%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-rare-earth-minerals-stockpile-mystery-opacity-worries-experts-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecritical%20mineral%3C%2Fa%3E%20imports%2C%20for%20example%2C%20argued%20that%20the%20US%20is%20overly%20dependent%20on%20foreign%20sources%20for%20materials%20essential%20to%20defense%2C%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20innovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeLong%20said%20that%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20there%20are%20at%20least%20eight%20ongoing%20Section%20232%20investigations%2C%20including%20those%20involving%20copper%2C%20timber%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdream-news-tech-sector-trump-announces-tariff-exemptions-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esemiconductors%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20said%20the%20recent%20June%203%20tariff%20hike%20on%20steel%20and%20aluminum%20from%2025%25%20to%2050%25%20is%20also%20being%20done%20under%20section%20232.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJones%20said%2C%20however%2C%20that%20each%20section%20232%20tariff%20requires%20a%20formal%20investigation%2C%20and%20the%20sectors%20it%20could%20be%20applied%20to%20are%20limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20problem%20with%20section%20232%20is%20that%20it%20requires%20a%20separate%20action%20for%20each%20industrial%20category%20of%20goods%20against%20which%20tariffs%20can%20be%20imposed%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jones.%20%26quot%3BThe%20perceived%20advantage%20of%20the%20IEEPA%20was%20that%20it%20allowed%20broad%20tariff%20coverage%20across%20the%20board%20to%20all%20industries.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ac7f69e2-b013-411c-a63d-fb31c0d204c7%5C%22%3ESection%20301%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESection%20301%20of%20the%20Trade%20Act%20of%201974%20gives%20the%20US%20Trade%20Representative%20%E2%80%94%20now%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-china-trade-deal-agreement-slash-trump-tariffs-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJamieson%20Greer%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebroad%20authority%20to%20investigate%20whether%20other%20countries%20are%20violating%20existing%20trade%20agreements%20or%20hurting%20American%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeLong%20said%20that%20the%20first%20Trump%20administration%20leaned%20heavily%20on%20the%20provision%20to%20impose%20tariffs%20on%20hundreds%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20worth%20of%20Chinese%20goods%20and%20aircraft%20from%20the%20European%20Union.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-begins-section-301-investigation-2017-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esection%20301%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20require%20a%20formal%20investigation%20and%20even%20a%20public%20comment%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20problem%20with%20sec.%20301%2C%20however%2C%20is%20that%20it%20requires%20a%20separate%20determination%20of%20specific%20foreign%20unfair%20or%20discriminatory%20trade%20practices%2C%20country%20by%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20IEEPA%2C%20again%2C%20seemed%20to%20give%20the%20President%20mor