ing%20the%20farm%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-06T173338.338-1749211432.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-06T173338.338-1749211432-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-06T173338.338-1749211432-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-06T173338.338-1749211432-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-06T173338.338-1749211432-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-445479%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20international%20recognition%20pushed%20Dimum%20to%20focus%20more%20reviving%20such%20lost%20millets%20and%20vegetables.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20took%20some%20of%20my%20products%20there%20and%20it%20was%20quite%20interesting%20to%20across%20people%20from%20different%20ethnicities%20coming%20together%20with%20different%20ideas%20It%20was%20a%20big%20exposure%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20to%20her%20surprise%2C%20people%20were%20genuinely%20curious%20about%20her%20millet.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20carried%20two%20packets%20of%20the%20millet%20and%20they%20bought%20both%20of%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%20Dimum%20is%20also%20in%20touch%20with%20a%20fellow%20delegate%20from%20the%20expo%20who%20is%20interested%20in%20procuring%20more%20of%20the%20revived%20millet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFor%20the%20joy%20of%20reviving%20lost%20foods%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20just%20two%20years%2C%20Gepo%20Aali%20has%20garnered%20around%20150%20loyal%20customers%20from%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%E2%80%94%20a%20sma