%20India%20needs%20a%20structured%20drug%20take-back%20system%20led%20by%20the%20government%20and%20supported%20by%20pharmacies%20and%20hospitals.%20Countries%20like%20the%20United%20States%20and%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20have%20well-established%20systems%20where%20residents%20can%20return%20unused%20medicines%20at%20designated%20collection%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerala%20has%20become%20the%20first%20state%20in%20the%20country%20to%20implement%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fkerala-to-launch-first-ever-project-on-collection-disposal-of-expired-medicines%2Farticleshow%2F118375784.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98nPROUD%E2%80%99%20project%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20designed%20to%20scientifically%20collect%20and%20safely%20dispose%20of%20expired%20and%20unused%20medicines.%20Launched%20by%20the%20State%20Drugs%20Control%20Department%2C%20the%20initiative%20%E2%80%98nPROUD%E2%80%99%20(New%20Programme%20for%20Removal%20of%20Unused%20Drugs)%20will%20facilitate%20the%20collection%20of%20unused%20medicines%20from%20households%20and%20ensure%20their%20proper%20disposal%20at%20designated%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUntil%20then%2C%20awareness%20is%20key.%20Pharmacists%2C%20healthcare%20workers%2C%20and%20citizens%20must%20be%20informed%20about%20the%20environmental%20and%20health%20hazards%20of%20improper%20medicine%20disposal.%20Educational%20institutions%20like%20Vivekananda%20Education%20Society%20(VES)%20College%20of%20Pharmacy%20are%20already%20trying%20to%20spread%20this%20message%20through%20student-led%20outreach%20programmes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20each%20of%20us%20makes%20the%20effort%20to%20dispose%20of%20medicines%20the%20right%20way%2C%20we%20contribute%20to%20a%20cleaner%2C%20healthier%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20the%20next%20time%20you%20open%20your%20medicine%20drawer%20and%20spot%20an%20expired%20tablet%20stri