LGBTQ%2B%20community.%20After%20all%2C%20there%20is%20no%20single%20way%20to%20be%20LGBTQ%2B%20and%20definitely%20no%20one-size-fits-all%20way%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20identities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20can%20be%20done%20while%20being%20respectful%3F%20Simply%20ask.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsk%20people%20how%20they%20describe%20themselves%2C%20ask%20for%20their%20pronouns%2C%20and%20reflect%20that%20in%20how%20you%20speak%20about%20them%20or%20write%20about%20them.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20language%20is%20about%20listening%2C%20and%20this%20guide%20is%20just%20a%20starting%20point%20to%20help%20us%20all%20do%20that%20a%20little%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELGBTQ%2B%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20start%20with%20the%20foundation.%20You%E2%80%99ve%20probably%20seen%20the%20acronym%20LGBTQ%20used%20often%2C%20whether%20in%20conversations%2C%20news%2C%20or%20on%20social%20media.%20It%20stands%20for%20lesbian%2C%20gay%2C%20bisexual%2C%20transgender%2C%20and%20queer.%20Sometimes%2C%20especially%20in%20youth-focused%20spaces%2C%20the%20Q%20can%20also%20mean%20questioning%20because%20figuring%20things%20out%20takes%20time%2C%20and%20that%20is%20okay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20might%20also%20see%20versions%20like%20LGBTQ%2B%2C%20with%20the%20plus%20added%20to%20be%20more%20inclusive%20of%20all%20identities%20that%20don%E2%80%99t%20fall%20under%20%E2%80%9Cstraight%E2%80%9D%20or%