%2C%20and%2For%20physically%20attracted%20to%20people%20of%20the%20same%20gender.%20It%20is%20most%20commonly%20used%20for%20men%20(as%20in%20gay%20men)%2C%20but%20some%20women%20also%20use%20the%20word%20to%20describe%20themselves%20(gay%20women%20or%20gay%20people).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20just%20like%20with%20lesbians%2C%20try%20to%20avoid%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98homosexual%E2%80%99%20as%20it%20feels%20clinical%20and%20impersonal%20to%20many%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBisexual%2C%20Bi%2C%20Bi%2B%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20bisexual%20means%20that%20someone%20can%20feel%20emotionally%2C%20romantically%2C%20or%20physically%20attracted%20to%20more%20than%20one%20gender.%20This%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20mean%20they%E2%80%99re%20always%20attracted%20to%20all%20genders%20equally%20or%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20It%20just%20means%20that%20their%20attraction%20isn%E2%80%99t%20limited%20to%20one%20gender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%9Cbi%E2%80%9D%20in%20bisexual%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20mean%20%E2%80%9Cmen%20and%20women%E2%80%9D.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20refers%20to%20attraction%20to%20people%20of%20your%20own%20gender%20and%20other%20genders.%20That%E2%80%99s%20an%20important%20difference!%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20might%20use%20the%20terms%20bi%2C%20bisexual%2C%20or%20bi%2B%20(which%20is%20meant%20to%20be%20more%20inclusive%20of%20identities%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F354604%2Ftransgender-business-owners-pride-month-chandigarh-soul-spectrum-ishnoor-singh-dhananjay-chauhan-pride-month%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epansexual%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20queer%2C%20or%20fluid%20%E2%80%94%