%20people%20and%20their%20lives%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20word%20%E2%80%9Clifestyle%E2%80%9D%20usually%20describes%20the%20way%20people%20choose%20to%20live%2C%20like%20being%20busy%2C%20relaxed%2C%20eco-friendly%2C%20or%20sporty.%20It%20is%20about%20personal%20choices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20people%20say%20%E2%80%9CLGBT%20lifestyle%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20wrongly%20suggests%20that%20being%20gay%2C%20lesbian%2C%20bi%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F436107%2Fbabli-by-night-bafta-neel-soni%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrans%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20choice%2C%20like%20picking%20a%20hobby%20or%20a%20trend.%20Being%20LGBTQI%2B%20is%20not%20a%20lifestyle%3B%20rather%2C%20it%20is%20who%20someone%20is.%20LGBTQI%2B%20people%20can%20have%20all%20kinds%20of%20lives%3A%20some%20are%20married%2C%20some%20have%20kids%2C%20some%20are%20single%2C%20and%20they%20live%20in%20all%20kinds%20of%20ways%2C%20just%20like%20anyone%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EDon%E2%80%99t%20say%20%E2%80%9Csex%20reassignment%20surgery%2C%E2%80%9D%20say%20%E2%80%9Ctransitioning%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETransition%20is%20the%20personal%20process%20that%20someone%20goes%20through%20to%20help%20their%20gender%20expression%20and%2For%20their%20body%20better%20match%20their%20gender%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20might%20include%20hormone%20therapy%20or%20surgeries.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20better%20to%20avoid%20terms%20like%20%E2%80%9Csex%20reassignment%20surgery%2C%E2%80%9D%20which%20can%20sound%20outdated%20or%20overly%20focused%20on%20the%20body.%20Instead%2C%20just%20say%20%E2%80%9Ctransition%E2%80%9D%2C%20or%20talk%20about%20it%20in%20terms%20the%20person%20uses%3Cem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESide%20note%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETransitioning%20is%20not%20just%20about%20medical%20changes.%20It%20can%20also%20include%20social%20and%20legal%20steps.%20This%20might%20mean%20coming%20out%20to%20family%20and%20friends%2C%20using%20a%20new%20name%20or%20pronouns%2C%20or%20changing%20how%20one%20dresses%20to%20reflect%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F248393%2Ffirst-transgender-band-yash-raj-films-komal-jagtap-transgender-rights-inspiring-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egender%20identity%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20can%20also%20involve%20updating%20documents%20like%20one%E2%80%99s%20driver%E2%80%99s%20license%2C%20passport%20and%20bank%20account%20to%20match%20the%20name%20and%20gender.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20transition%20is%20personal%2C%20and%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20one%20%E2%80%9Cright%E2%80%9D%20way%20to%20do%20it%20%E2%80%94%20just%20the%20way%20that%20feels%20right!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPride%20Month%20is%20a%20time%20to%20celebrate%2C%20but%20it%20is%20also%20a%20moment%20to%20listen%2C%20learn%2C%20and%20grow.%20Understanding%20the%20words%20people%20use%20to%20describe%20themselves%20helps%20us%20show%20respect%20and%20kindness%20every%20day%2C%20not%20just%20in%20June.%20Let%20us%20embrace%20language%20with%20care%2C%20thus%20opening%20doors%20to%20acceptance%20and%20connection%2C%20helping%20everyone%20feel%20seen%20and%20valued%20just%20as%20they%20are!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Leila%20Badyari%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749193961000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FTBI-featured-image-5-1749189686.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D445073%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20you%E2%80%99ve%20ever%20hesitated%20to%20ask%20what%20%26quot%3Bqueer%E2%80%9D%20means%20%E2%80%94%20this%20glossary%20is%20for%20you.%20In%20collaboration%20with%20The%20Humsafar%20Trust%2C%20we%20broke%20down%20key%20LGBTQ%2B%20terms%20respectfully.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%