arents%20knew%20this.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20simply%20forgotten%20in%20our%20rush%20to%20modernity.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20wait%20for%20the%20system%20to%20catch%20up%2C%20BCML%20is%20co-creating%20the%20solution.%20The%20company%20is%20partnering%20with%20governments%20to%20run%20model%20projects%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F262364%2Fdr-bio-bio-compostable-plastic-corn-starch-straw-buy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecomposting%20and%20chemical%20recycling%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20showing%20that%20circular%20systems%20can%20be%20implemented%20not%20just%20in%20controlled%20labs%20or%20global%20capitals%2C%20but%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20rural%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20launch%20of%20the%20brand%20Balrampur%20Bioyug%2C%20where%20the%20plant%20is%20set%20to%20be%20commissioned%20by%20October%202026%2C%20not%20only%20marks%20a%20decisive%20leap%20in%20sustainable%20manufacturing%20but%20also%20signals%20a%20significant%20shift%20in%20how%20India%20approaches%20material%20innovation%20for%20a%20circular%2C%20cleaner%2C%20greener%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Stefan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20story%20about%20innovation%20and%20alignment%20between%20farmer%20and%20factory%2C%20product%20and%20planet%2C%20and%20industry%20and%20intention.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECan%20India%20become%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20biochemical%20hub%3F%20Absolutely.%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20something%20the%20world%20desperately%20needs%3A%20biomass%20and%20intent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99re%20a%20biomass-rich%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Avantika.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20already%20have%20the%20raw%20material%20in%20abundance.%20We%20could%20even%20become%20the%20bioplastic%20and%20biochemical%20hub%20of%20the%20world.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStefan%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20lot%2